thread.title_full: ScreenPrinting.com reviewed by Prai Nanowear Inc.

author: Prai Nanowear Inc.
title: Prai Nanowear Inc.
text:
I have been a customer with Ryonet for 6 years for wearable electronics prototyping.
They have very good resources for first time screen printers. They also have a wide network of suppliers/vendors that can provide equipment for the next step in scaling up micro supply chains.
